article_title: Feds want proof for ACA exchange special enrollment windows
article_text: By Tom Murphy, The Associated Press

article_metadata.description: The federal government is tightening loopholes that let customers on the Affordable Care Act's public insurance exchanges buy coverage outside the law's annual enrollment window.
article_metadata.author: Tom Murphy, The Associated Press
